    "en": {
      "title": "Sudden fire at Ragala's house; Three rescues",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police said that a separate house in Mandirithenna village under Rakala police division was caught fire at three o'clock in the morning today (15).",
        "Suspecting that the fire may have been caused by an electrical fault, the Rakala police said that only three people, including two children and their mother, were in the house at the time of the incident, and they were rescued safely.",
        "The fire was brought under control as the neighbors rushed to the house and heard the screams of the house on fire.",
        "A portion of the house including the roof and the bedroom has caught fire and clothes and furniture have also partially caught fire, Rakala Police said."
      ],
